picks some people. Some are very active posters others just now and 
then but the run on replys it attaches to bottom may be to blame. I 
dont get blocked here when I dont delete whats below but I get 
blocked on other boards and have to wait til a mod approves it. It&#39;s 
no big deal I am in and out anyway so by the time I get off work its 
